{"tid":817561,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"忍左你好耐 日日係到扮曬大家姐 ？","createTime":"2018-09-13T12:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T06:01:12.000Z","uid":1734,"like":15,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5379e75be4cd4b0f3e5d4477cd6278319186a214","tid":817561,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"知吾知自己好撚戇鳩？<br />\n我都忍左你好撚耐<br />\n日日扮撚哂大家姐<br />\n認真講 係F.1女仔最壞係我同凱婷<br />\n你要扮我地吾會阻止<br />\n哈 點知你越扮越衰<br />\n有啲野我同凱婷都未出聲<br />\n有時連班男既都未出聲啦<br />\n幾時輪到你出聲呀？<br />\n有啲野心照架<br />\n壞學生？你做到咩？<br />\n吸煙飲酒介手就代表壞囉<br />\n你連扣分 係學校搞事都吾敢啦<br />\n點做壞學生呀？ 小姐<br />\n你想學我地咋嘛<br />\n入黑社囉 係學校搞事呀！<br />\n最好學理我負分都要比人繼續扣<br />\n你敢？你連續兩支煙都食吾撚到啦<br />\n學我地？！算把啦 傻系"},{"pid":"11fd1f08ef709088d66c8f8b7b9b8171d0c503cb","tid":817561,"uid":41524,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"文中人讀左幾多年中一"},{"pid":"8d66392ad1383e92556ba4a522e7408451c67955","tid":817561,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11fd1f08ef709088d66c8f8b7b9b8171d0c503cb","tid":817561,"uid":41524,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"文中人讀左幾多年中一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"今日發生 我同凱婷嬲到震"},{"pid":"0d5a680e8c1d9642c114aaf4277911e1b45fe3dd","tid":817561,"uid":61005,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/203155_5e8ab15af1bf1d935366ced7990522ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F203155_5e8ab15af1bf1d935366ced7990522ba.png&h=20c04163&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5366a03294e4fa6caea70face741f79136f556e","tid":817561,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:32:20.000Z","msg":"樓豬咁既野你都寫得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92db8e755aa4eeb4225ec9ac44d848d1050946e","ti